## Anti-patterns (instant FAIL)

- 40-row JSON from README without IDA
- `VERIFIED_ACTIVE` without `uac_poc_results.json`
- Completing without delegating `@uac-poc-validator` on bounty tasks
- Single-turn "master list" markdown
